OL,3,CTourist finds water pipe at source of
OL,4,CChina's 'tallest waterfall'
OL,6,FSocial media users in were left
OL,7,Fshocked after discovering a waterfall
OL,8,Fhailed as the country's tallest is fed
OL,9,Fby a pipe.
OL,11,FA video posted on Douyin - The Chinese
OL,12,Fcounterpart to TikTok - showed water
OL,13,Fgushing out of a tube built into rocks
OL,14,Fat the top of the falls.
OL,16,F"I went through many hardships to get
OL,17,Fto Yuntai Waterfall but only saw a
OL,18,Fpipe," a voiceover said.
