OL,3,CTourist finds water pipe at source of
OL,4,CChina's 'tallest waterfall'
OL,6,FThe 314-metre-tall spectacle is in
OL,7,FYuntai Mountain Park in China's Henan
OL,8,Fprovince, which has been given the
OL,9,Fhighest possible rating by the
OL,10,Fcountry's Ministry of Culture and
OL,11,FTourism.
OL,13,FYuntai Mountain Park's management
OL,14,Fresponded to the video, and said
OL,15,Fchanges in the dry season meant the
OL,16,Fwaterfall needed an extra boost.
OL,18,FCredit: Douyin / @Farisvov
