OL,3,CTourist finds water pipe at source of
OL,4,CChina's 'tallest waterfall'
OL,6,F"The waterfall cannot guarantee to
OL,7,Fmeet the public in its most beautiful
OL,8,Fappearance due to season changes,"
OL,9,Fthey said, adding that it underwent "a
OL,10,Ftiny improvement during dry season."
OL,12,FManagement promised the waterfall
OL,13,Fwould be ready for guests this summer
OL,14,Fin its "most perfect and most natural
OL,15,Fform."
OL,17,FThe revelation shocked some social
OL,18,Fmedia users, but others were more
OL,19,Fsympathetic.
